notes_display: In Historical Sketches of the Paper Currency of the American Colonies by Henry Phillips, Jr. (1865). Given to Dr. Jesse C. Green in 1890. Leaf 56CI.
issue_obverse_legend_s: EIGHTEEN PENCE. THIS Indented BILL shall pass current for EIGHTEEN PENCE, according to an Act of General Assembly of the Counties of Newcastle, Kent and Sussex, upon Delaware, passed in the 15th Year of the Reign of His Majesty George the IIId. Dated the First Day of January, 1776.
issue_reverse_legend_s: EIGHTEEN PENCE. To Counterfeit is Death. Printed by JAMES ADAMS, 1776
